OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy throughout with an
OL,6,Finitial risk of low cloud and fog near
OL,7,Fthe Lincolnshire coast. Patchy light
OL,8,Frain is possible early on, before
OL,9,Fbecoming mostly dry from late morning.
OL,10,FWinds generally light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly cloudy overnight with
OL,13,Fpatches of drizzle in the south.
OL,14,FFurther north, a few clear spells may
OL,15,Fdevelop later, where a frost along
OL,16,Fwith some fog patches are possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
