OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FPerhaps some brightness in
OL,6,Fthe north initially once any fog
OL,7,Fpatches clear, but otherwise a cloudy
OL,8,Fday with patches of rain and drizzle,
OL,9,Falong with light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMurky
OL,12,Fwith low cloud and patchy drizzle
OL,13,FSunday. Dull initially Monday, but
OL,14,Fbrighter spells soon developing along
OL,15,Fwith a risk of showers. Some
OL,16,Fbrightness initially Tuesday but
OL,17,Fbecoming increasingly cloudy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
